thread.title: Harpreet

author: Harpreet
title: Harpreet
text: Highly satisfied with their customer care, especially Candace and Clairissa. I had originally ordered the wrong contacts and they were more than happy to send me a return label right away with overnight shipping. Then, I forgot to include the return authorization form with box and they were willing to keep track of the package and emailed me as soon as the package arrived. I was able to get the correct ones 2 days later.
